## hello there!

### it seems that you've found yourself here with me.
as you can see, there's not too much to look at.  Let's see what I can entertain you with...

* my twitter's a bit more dynamic - [@msherico] (http://twitter.com/msherico)
* and I post interesting things from time to time on my [tumblr](http://missherico.tumblr.com) - [missherico.tumblr.com] (http://missherico.tumblr.com)
* oh! and I love love [foursquare] (https://foursquare.com/user/5493713) - [my badges] (https://foursquare.com/user/5493713)
    * see, I even make [lists] (https://foursquare.com/user/5493713/lists/created)


great great, now you've something to busy yourself with while i do some home improvements around here. go on, enjoy my foursquare lists, they're top notch.
tagline: holding isa's hodge podge of digital interests
